Package: ssdeR
Type: Package
Title: Sample selection models with a common dummy endogenous regressor in simultaneous equations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Brottrager", email = "michael.brottrager@gmx.net",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Michael Brottrager <michael.brottrager@gmx.net>
Description: Estimates sample selection models where a common dummy endogenous regressor appears both in the selection equation and in the censored equation. We interpret this model as an endogenous switching model and develop a simple two step estimation procedure.
License:  GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: miscTools, systemfit, Formula, VGAM, mvtnorm, maxLik, fBasics, sandwich, zoo
Suggests: lmtest, dplyr
